          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "With millions of Americans trapped at home to protect themselves from a deadly pandemic during the holiday season, the Internet is one of the only conduits connecting them to friends, family and the outside world. Now, Comcast, one of the monopoly corporations that controls the conduit, is ",
